        "setup": "Use an MCP client that supports OAuth and connect to the Superhuman Mail MCP endpoint at `https://mcp.mail.superhuman.com/mcp`. Superhuman's help flow shows adding the server in an MCP client and then choosing **Authenticate**, which opens a browser sign-in flow for your Superhuman Mail account. You need a Superhuman Mail account with Ask AI enabled, the Superhuman Mail Chrome extension for authentication, and a Business plan or higher; some Enterprise accounts also require admin enablement. See [Superhuman Mail MCP Server help](https://help.superhuman.com/hc/en-us/articles/46005696690317-Superhuman-Mail-MCP-Server) and the [Mail MCP product page](https://superhuman.com/products/mail/mcp)."
